    <svcproc svcproctype="proctype" graphiccount="1">
        <title>ENGINE SHUTDOWN SYSTEM (FIGURE
            <hotlnk xrefid="ef1250803">1.32</hotlnk>)
        </title>
        <para>This system shuts down the engine after 30 seconds of operation beyond critical threshold values for
            coolant temperature, oil pressure and/or engine coolant level. The above mentioned warning system is
            included with this shutdown system. The engine may be restarted after shutdown, if it is mechanically
            capable of starting.
        </para>
